{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"454","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"經部將設綠電直售交易市場","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='background: white; margin: 0px; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;'><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(141, 141, 141); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;'>2019-05-04 01:30</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(141, 141, 141); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 10pt;'>經濟日報</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(141, 141, 141); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;'> </span><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(141, 141, 141); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 10pt;'>記者江睿智、葉卉軒／台北報導</span></p>\n\n<p style='background: white; margin: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 0%; text-indent: -18pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;'><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;'><span style='margin: 0px;'>&middot;<span style='font: 7pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='background: white; margin: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 0%; text-indent: -18pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;'><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;'><span style='margin: 0px;'>&middot;<span style='font: 7pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='background: white; margin: 20px 0px; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;'><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>《再生能源發展條例》修正案</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>1</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>日公告實施，經濟部將建立綠電直售交易市場，滿足產業界購買綠電需求。經濟部長沈榮津昨（</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>3</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>）日表示，已要求工業局、台電詳細盤點需求面及供給面，盡速掌握綠電供給情形。目前初步掌握，綠電供給大於需求。</span></p>\n\n<p style='background: white; margin: 20px 0px; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;'><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>沈榮津昨日上午出席「</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>2019</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>第</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>38</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>屆新一代設計展」時表示，已先請台電依修正後的《再生能源發展條例》盡速修正相關合約，使未來新加入業者可以在躉購及直供轉供制度間自由轉換，同時就過去已簽約的案件研議合理解約作法，近期會就相關執行細節再釐清。</span></p>\n\n<p style='background: white; margin: 20px 0px; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;'><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>沈榮津表示，綠電需求可能來自法規要求、環評承諾、產業綠色供應鏈要求或企業社會責任，工業局將邀相關產業公協會及廠商進行需求盤點。</span></p>\n\n<p style='background: white; margin: 20px 0px; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;'><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>在供給面部分，沈榮津指示台電分別針對再生能源業者的簽約、併網及取得電業執照等不同時間點，盤點裝置容量及發電量，確保業者未來可以買到所需綠電。</span></p>\n\n<p style='background: white; margin: 20px 0px; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;'><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>此外，因台電本身肩負節能減碳義務，負有降低排碳係數法定責任，一旦釋出過多綠電可能無法達標；對此，沈榮津表示，這也已經請台電檢討，但初步看來，供給遠大於台電本身的目標量。</span></p>\n\n<p style='background: white; margin: 20px 0px; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;'><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>同時，能源局也將就《再生能源發展條例》修正後，需設置一定比例再生能源的用戶範圍、設置比例及期程等，邀請利害關係人及地方政府共同研擬完整配套作法，以建立綠電自由交易市場。</span></p>\n\n<p style='background: white; margin: 20px 0px; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;'><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>還有，經濟部次長曾文生也提到，如今台灣再生能源在市場上逐漸具有競爭力，尤其全球環保意識抬頭，暖化問題受重視，未來要把產品賣到國際，就要採用一定比例再生能源，且政府已規劃</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>2025</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>年再生能源發電占比</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>20%</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>目標，未來綠能科技就業機會必逐年增加，亦是未來就業新趨勢。</span></p>\n\n<p style='background: white; margin: 20px 0px; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;'><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>曾文生指出，過去講到能源產業，大概就是中油、台電兩家公司，但未來情況大不同，</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>2000</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>年以前進口能源總值占</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>GDP</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>不到</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>5%</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>，</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>2010</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>年以後進口能源總值占</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>GDP</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>超過</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>10%</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>。換句話說，台灣每生產</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>10</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>元就要花</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>1</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>元買燃料，過去台灣能源高度仰賴進口是因為再生能源技術還不成熟，如今再生能源在市場逐漸具競爭力，未來綠能科技就業機會必逐年增加，可看出此產業對國家未來的重要性。</span></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px;'><span style='margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;新細明體&quot;,serif;'>資料來源：</span><span style='margin: 0px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px;'><a href='https://money.udn.com/money/story/7307/3792418'><font color='#0000ff' face='Calibri'>https://money.udn.com/money/story/7307/3792418</font></a></span></span></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2019-05-09","clk_count":"195"}},"__N_SSG":true}